# `.gitignore` (Industry Standard for Spring Boot)

```gitignore
# Maven
target/
*.log

# Java
*.class
*.jar
*.war

# IDE
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
.vscode/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Spring Boot
*.pid
*.seed

# Environment
.env

# Node (if frontend added later)
node_modules/

# Build
build/
out/